'''Sien'Soro''' were a band during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] who were able to escape a [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatist]] blockade with the help of [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Darrus Jeht/Legends|Darrus Jeht]]. They repaid him with backstage passes to several upcoming concerts.

